Name: Jump Jump
About the game: 'Jump Jump' is a casual game. Play by jumping with the help of the operator. Jumping onto the box counts as 1 point, and jumping into the middle of the box counts as 2 points. [Game Operation] Click the mouse on the screen to start accumulating force. Release the mouse and the villain will jump. [Game features] The distance of the villain's jump will be determined according to the length of the force accumulation time. The longer the force accumulation time is, the farther he will jump. It takes skill to get high marks. The game is easy and fast, which is suitable for playing in leisure time.
